---
import PageShell from "../components/PageShell.astro";
---

<PageShell title="About | The Things We Build in 48 Hours">
  <section class="page-hero container">
    <h1 class="serif">A builder learning in public, one deadline at a time.</h1>
    <p>
      Sayyid Khan is a Singapore-based AI builder and software engineer
      documenting his journey to complete one hundred hackathons while searching
      for purpose through the things he builds.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="section rail">
    <div class="container split">
      <h2 class="serif">Why hackathons?</h2>
      <div>
        <p>
          Hackathons make ambition visible. They turn vague interests into
          prototypes, teams into pressure systems, and ideas into moments where
          someone else can finally react.
        </p>
        <p>
          This site exists to keep the full record: the idea, the people, the
          chaos, the build, the failure, the win, and the lesson.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section container beliefs">
    <h2 class="serif">Operating Beliefs</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Building is a form of self-discovery.</li>
      <li>Repetition creates luck.</li>
      <li>Shipping reveals truth.</li>
      <li>Failure compounds into instinct.</li>
      <li>Purpose is discovered through motion.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</PageShell>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    padding: 78px 0 90px;
  }

  h1 {
    max-width: 980px;
    margin: 0;
    font-size: clamp(3.3rem, 8vw, 8.5rem);
    line-height: 0.9;
  }

  .page-hero p {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 28px 0 0;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .split {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 0.7fr) minmax(300px, 0.85fr);
    gap: 42px;
  }

  h2 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 5vw, 5.4rem);
    line-height: 0.95;
  }

  p {
    margin: 0 0 18px;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .beliefs ul {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(5, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 12px;
    margin: 32px 0 0;
    padding: 0;
    list-style: none;
  }

  li {
    min-height: 150px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.55;
    padding-top: 18px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .split,
    .beliefs ul {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
